{"tid":675882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾美利換logo示忠 Emery發音似Emirates","createTime":"2018-05-24T02:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T04:49:01.000Z","uid":30040,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ec899831816ee7fdee1f2fdae308220125d2545a","tid":675882,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbok%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=dcf41d2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】新時代來臨，阿仙奴新領隊艾美利已急不及待向天下兵迷示好，深受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n46歲西班牙人艾美利（Unai Emery）取代雲加，成為阿仙奴新帥，馬上Twitter更換logo，用上球會的會徽，同時更新了個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n艾美利急不及待展開新里程，在官方消息發佈後，已把所在地由巴黎改為倫敦，暫時看來甚得兵迷歡迎，更有網民列出近5季的捧盃數量，這位兵工廠主帥已有10冠，比起哥迪奧拿的9冠更厲害。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，<span style=\"color: red;\">兵迷自行「發現」</span>艾美利與阿仙奴的緣份，像22年前的雲加一樣，相信這是天作之合。雲加的名字Arsene，與阿仙奴的名字Arsenal只差一個字母，同樣地，艾美利的姓氏Emery，與酋長球場Emirates的發音非常相似，令人覺得他是真命天子。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edc7aea6bde3363344749c80d64a792de32fb9c","tid":675882,"uid":126044,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"成班阿狗輸波輸到懞撚左"},{"pid":"aff6b34d851e991f14eae9bc3ba54265a15892f9","tid":675882,"uid":20473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"天降祥瑞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2998d00d168001dea7a987db995f760f139b8ec7","tid":675882,"uid":15830,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"Emery Stadium<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606e56bb60fd971f26252779cdf1e1c12997d9a5","tid":675882,"uid":76681,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">迷自行「發現」艾美利與阿仙奴的緣份，</span>像22年前的雲加一樣，相信這是天作之合。雲加的名字Arsene，與阿仙奴的名字Arsenal只差一個字母，<span style=\"c